LOCUS       ALFA_tag                  13 aa            linear   UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  ALFA_tag — a 13-aa synthetic epitope tag (SRLEEELRRRLTE) recognized
            by the NbALFA nanobody with ultra-high affinity (Kd = 26 pM), used
            for protein detection, purification, and imaging..
